nodes.text: Sor Cin'da was a male individual who operated as a code-breaker in the Anoat sector. At some point during the Iron Blockade, the Trade Spine League intercepted coded Imperial data, which only Cin'da could decode. However, he was known to be surly and wary of strangers.
At the League's behest, the Smuggler dispatched some of their crewmembers to persuade the code-breaker to collaborate.
